---
import { APP_URL_V3 } from '@/config/github';
const base = (typeof import.meta.env.BASE_URL === 'string' && import.meta.env.BASE_URL) || '/';
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 sm:py-28 lg:py-36" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_80%_60%_at_50%_-20%,rgba(14,165,233,0.25),transparent)]" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-400">Die führende europäische Alternative zu Kahoot & Mentimeter</p>
    <h1 id="hero-heading" class="font-display text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
      Quizzen, abstimmen.<br />
      <span class="text-brand-400">Gemeinsam und live.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-300 sm:text-xl">
      Kostenlos · DSGVO-orientiert · Open Source. Kein Account, keine Abos. <strong class="text-white">Eine Startseite für Lehrende und Teilnehmende</strong> – Quiz, Live-Abstimmung und Q&amp;A mit Code oder QR. Inhalte bleiben bei dir (Local-First); Session-Daten temporär und selbst gehostet per Docker. Kita bis Uni, Presets von seriös bis spielerisch.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4" id="start">
      <a href={APP_URL_V3} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-brand-500 px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30 transition hover:bg-brand-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-400 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-slate-900">
        <img src={`${base}favicon.svg`} alt="" class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0" width="20" height="20" />
        Jetzt testen (Beta)
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}#vertrauen`} class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border border-slate-600 bg-slate-800/50 px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur transition hover:border-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-800">
        Bewertungen aus Forschung & Praxis
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}#vergleich`} class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl border border-slate-600 bg-slate-800/50 px-6 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur transition hover:border-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-800">
        Mit Kahoot & Mentimeter vergleichen
      </a>
    </div>
    <ul class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 text-sm text-slate-400" role="list">
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> Live-Quiz · Q&amp;A · Code &amp; QR</li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> Presets · Team-Modus · Anonym</li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> Lesephase · Peer Instruction · Word Cloud</li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> Rangliste · Streak · Bonus-Code</li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> Local-First · Yjs-Sync · Import/Export</li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> KI-Import (extern, Zod) · 5 Sprachen</li>
      <li class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true" /> Self-Host · Admin &amp; Audit für Betrieb</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
